## Instructions: 

```js
npm install whats_wrong
const whats_wrong =  require('whats_wrong')
```

## If utilizing in html...: 
```html
<script src="./node_modules/whats_wrong/index.js"></script>
<script> 
$(()=> { 
     const output =  whats_wrong.method(parameter)
 })
</script>
```
